          "type": "text",
          "text": "usp_Processing_InvoiceBillingGroupPreProcessingDetail",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to generate a summary report of invoice billing groups for a specific utility company and billing period. It aggregates financial data such as previous balances, payments received, current charges, late charges, and total amounts due. Additionally, it counts the number of invoices and adjustments for each billing group. The results are intended to be displayed in a data grid, providing a detailed view of the billing status for each group associated with a utility company."
        }
